Detailed Description

template<typename T, class LOCK, class TRAITS = traits, class ALLOCATOR = CDS_DEFAULT_ALLOCATOR>
class cds::queue::RWQueue< T, LOCK, TRAITS, ALLOCATOR >

Michael & Scott blocking queue with fine-grained synchronization schema.

Member Function Documentation

template<typename T , class LOCK , class TRAITS = traits, class ALLOCATOR = CDS_DEFAULT_ALLOCATOR>
bool cds::queue::RWQueue< T, LOCK, TRAITS, ALLOCATOR >::dequeue ( T &  dest ) [inline]

Dequeues a value to dest.

If queue is empty returns false, dest may be corrupted. If queue is not empty returns true, dest contains the value dequeued
